                     <interp inst="t17970920-7-person93" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I have known the prisoner about a year and a half, he has always been a very sober and industrious man since I have known him; he has a wife and three children, and his wife big again. <rs id="t17970920-7-verdict32" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970920-7-verdict32" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
